  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Reorganizing Business Partner Texts</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page topic  - topic-topic \" id=\"loio1cfbc5536a51204be10000000a174cb4\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Reorganizing Business Partner Texts </h1><div class=\"body\">\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Use\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">See <a class=\"xref\" href=\"69fac5536a51204be10000000a174cb4.html\">Performance Functions for Reporting</a>\n</p>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Procedure\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Procedure</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Call the function [transaction TRMP_PERFORMANCE_BP] ( <span class=\"ph\">path</span> ). The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Change View \"Temporary Text Table for Business Partner</span> s (Performance)\" appears.\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Select the data you want to delete. The following utilities are available to help you:\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">You can restrict the data volume by choosing <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Selection Criteria</span> → <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">By Contents</span> . The possible selection criteria include:\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Business partner\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Language Key\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Changed on\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Changed by\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">…\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">You can select all data or a certain block of data by choosing <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Edit</span> → <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Selections</span> .\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Choose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Edit</span> → <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Delete</span> to remove the selected lines from the table.\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Save your changes.\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">\n</p>\n</section></div>\n</div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
}